{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 246532,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「やいやいやい！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hey hey hey hey!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246533,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どうしたんだワーグ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "What's wrong, Warg?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246534,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そんな暗い顔ばっかしちまってー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Why are you wearing such a gloomy face?!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246535,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246536,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「俺みたいに明るく笑ってみろよ！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Try smiling brightly like me!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246537,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　わっはっはーってさ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Like, \"Wahaha!\"!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246538,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246539,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……ちぇっ、調子狂うなぁ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Tch, this is throwing me off."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246540,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ワーグが元気ないと、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If Warg’s not feeling cheerful,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246541,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　俺まで元気なくなっちまうよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "then even I lose my energy.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246542,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そのワーグを遙か遠くから",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "From far away, watching that Warg,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246543,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "眺めているのは、魔物の部隊だった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "was a troop of monsters."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246544,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あれが……魔人ワーグ様、か……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"So that's... Demon Warg-sama...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246545,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「噂には聞いていましたが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I've heard the rumors,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246546,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんとも凄まじい能力ですね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but that ability is truly terrifying...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246547,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ、貴様は派閥戦争では",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah, you weren’t assigned to Warg-sama's unit during the faction war,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246548,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ワーグ様の部隊には配属されてなかったか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "were you?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246549,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええ……話は伺っていましたが……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes... I've heard the stories, but..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246550,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　実際目の当たりにすると違いますな……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "seeing it in person is quite different..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246551,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　派閥戦争の決め手になったというのも、納得です」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I understand now why it was the decisive factor in the faction war.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246552,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「本人に戦闘力と呼べるものは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I hear that Warg himself has almost no combat ability..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246553,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　皆無に近いと聞きますが……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246554,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うむ、真に恐ろしいのはその能力よ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, the truly terrifying thing is that ability.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246555,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あの方の全身から溢れ出るフェロモンは、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The pheromones that overflow from his entire body"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246556,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　周囲の者を問答無用に眠らせ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "force everyone around him to fall asleep without question..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246557,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そして二度と目覚めさせない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and never wake them up again.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246558,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「嘘か誠か、帰ることの出来ぬ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It’s said—truth or not—that they are dragged"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246559,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　悪夢の世界に引きずり込まれるとか……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "into a nightmare world from which they cannot return...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246560,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「貴様らも、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You all,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246561,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あまり不用意に近づきすぎぬことだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "should not approach him carelessly.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246562,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔物将軍の言に隊長達は思わず唾を飲み込んだ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "At the monster general's words, the captains involuntarily swallowed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246563,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「眠る……と、聞けば……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Sleeping... when you hear that..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246564,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんともメルヘンですが……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "it sounds somewhat fairy tale-like...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246565,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ、二度と目覚めぬなら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, if they never awaken again,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246566,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　植物状態にするのとなんら変わらん」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "it's no different than putting them into a vegetative state.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246567,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いや、放置すれば死ぬのだ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, if left alone, they die."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246568,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　常に周囲が死ぬフェロモンを",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It’s like constantly emitting a pheromone that kills everything nearby..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246569,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　放っているようなものか……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246570,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「本人に破壊衝動などはないのに関わらず、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Although he himself lacks any destructive impulse,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246571,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　その能力だけで、ワーグ様はレッドアイ様や",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "just because of that ability alone, Warg-sama is feared like Red Eye-sama"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246572,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　メディウサ様と並び恐れられる方となった」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and Medusa-sama.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246573,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それほど……皆、あの能力には一目置いている。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"To that extent... everyone respects that ability."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246574,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔人である方々ですら、な」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Even those who are demons themselves.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246575,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「戦争では、砦に歩き近づくだけで話が済む。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"In war, just walking close to the fortress settles things."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246576,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　我々部下はその後、眠りこけている敵共を",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We subordinates just slaughter the enemies passed out afterward."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246577,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　屠殺するだけで勝てる……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That's all it takes to win...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246578,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔人同士の戦争さえ左右させる魔人ワーグ様だ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Demon Warg-sama, who influences even wars between demons,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246579,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　人間共に防ぐすなどない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "there is no way for humans to defend against him.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246580,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええ、先の派閥戦争において、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, in the recent faction war,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246581,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ワーグ様がケイブリス派を勝利に導いたと、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I now understand why it's rumored that Warg-sama led the Kaibriss faction to victory..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246582,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　噂される理由がよく分かりました……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246583,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……ん……ふう……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Hmm... phew...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246584,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "話している途中にもかかわらず、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Despite still talking,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246585,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔物隊長はコクリと首を傾かせた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the monster captain tilted his head drowsily."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246586,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ん？　どうした？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hm? What's wrong?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246587,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あっ、く……すみません……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, uh... sorry..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246588,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんだか、妙に……眠くて……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I suddenly feel... strangely sleepy...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246589,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ヒッ……！？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eek...!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246590,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "自分が発した、眠い、という単語に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Upon uttering the word 'sleepy',"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246591,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔物隊長はゾッと背筋を凍らせた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the monster captain felt a chill run down his spine."
    }
  ]
}

